 130:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c **** @verbatim   
 131:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
 132:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****                 ##### FLASH Erasing Programming functions ##### 
 133:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   ==============================================================================
 134:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c **** 
 135:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     [..] The FLASH Memory Erasing functions, includes the following functions:
 136:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     (+) HAL_FLASHEx_Erase: return only when erase has been done
 137:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     (+) HAL_FLASHEx_Erase_IT: end of erase is done when HAL_FLASH_EndOfOperationCallback 
 138:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****         is called with parameter 0xFFFFFFFF
 139:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c **** 
 140:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     [..] Any operation of erase should follow these steps:
 141:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     (#) Call the HAL_FLASH_Unlock() function to enable the flash control register and 
 142:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****         program memory access.
 143:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     (#) Call the desired function to erase page.
 144:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     (#) Call the HAL_FLASH_Lock() to disable the flash program memory access 
 145:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****        (recommended to protect the FLASH memory against possible unwanted operation).
 146:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c **** 
 147:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c **** @endverbatim
