 613:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     [..] Any operation of erase or program should follow these steps:
 614:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     (#) Call the HAL_FLASHEx_DATAEEPROM_Unlock() function to enable the data EEPROM access
 615:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****         and Flash program erase control register access.
