 617:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****     (#) Call the HAL_FLASHEx_DATAEEPROM_Lock() to disable the data EEPROM access
 618:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****         and Flash program erase control register access(recommended
 619:Drivers/STM32L0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l0xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****         to protect the DATA_EEPROM against possible unwanted operation).
